{"tid":781130,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"余德丞已醒！搵嘅第一個人係佢？","createTime":"2018-08-15T15:49:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T16:42:46.000Z","uid":86695,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bd916ccafa4064400f12d24c17d66177b44fd07d","tid":781130,"uid":86695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T15:49:04.000Z","msg":"藝人余德丞（Dickson）早前踢波暈倒送入瑪麗醫院深切治療部（ICU），日前其經理人透露Dickson已轉住心臟科病房觀察。呢日喺社交網亦終於再見到Dickson嘅蹤影，事關佢好友鄧佩儀（Gloria）上載一張咗台灣旅行歎珍珠奶茶嘅相，Dickson就留言：「THIS IS SUPER GOOD!!!!!!」即令網友表示好開心見到Dickson逐漸康復，並已經可以瀏覽社交網。至於Gloria亦有立即回覆Dickson，指好開心可以見到佢，仲祝佢早日康復。 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/15/234900_141bffb095f8a3ad016aa55bb2a3d87c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F15%2F234900_141bffb095f8a3ad016aa55bb2a3d87c.png&h=aec7d520&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd50be9f0befe5a92192a93f2446523757563838","tid":781130,"uid":73114,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T16:07:54.000Z","msg":"關我蛋治？"},{"pid":"101df5d31d5a76f0d62123dd3cf5b77de1011d7a","tid":781130,"uid":11713,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T16:42:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/16/004241_81d707d4e5fd884fc5ac10bf42a62d48.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F16%2F004241_81d707d4e5fd884fc5ac10bf42a62d48.png&h=e0e0df64&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}